Class AbstractPlugin

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class AbstractPlugin
extends Observable<PluginEvent>
implements ReaderPlugin, Nameable, Configurable
    Observable plugin. These plugin can report when a reader is added or removed.

      • initNativeReaders

        protected abstract java.util.SortedSet<SeReader> initNativeReaders()
                                                            throws KeypleReaderException
        Init connected native readers (from third party library) and returns a list of corresponding SeReader

        SeReader are new instances.

        this method is called once in the plugin constructor.

        Returns:
        the list of AbstractReader objects.
        Throws:
        KeypleReaderException - if a reader error when readers list initialization, it will be thrown by the constructor in a KeypleRuntimeException to be caught at a higher level by the AbstractPluginFactory
